author: Knowledge Zenith Store
title: Knowledge Zenith KZ ZSN Pro X earphone with mic
description:
Rp239.000 (10-07-2024)

KZ ZSN Pro X menggunakan silver plated cable dari yang sebelumnya yang menggunakan OFC (Oxygen Free Copper), penggunaan kabel silver plated copper biasanya menjadikan suara menjadi lebih jernih dan suara high / treble menjadi lebih ngecring.

author: Jaben Indonesia
title: 64audio Tia Fourte
description:
Rp46.800.000 (10-07-2024)

Fourté is the pinnacle of in-ear monitor technology. With its entire design being made up of industry firsts, Fourté isn’t just a four driver hybrid UIEM. The innovations of acoustically shaping micro-chambers, direct radiating drivers, and the single sound bore come together in our patented tia technology. Fourté is our first IEM to feature internally integrated patented apex technology. These along with its ergonomic shell, machined out of solid aluminum, have dictated our entire UIEM design language since its development in 2016.

author: csi-zone
title: Moondrop MAY Dynamic + Planar Driver IEM With DSP Type C Plug & Mic
description:
Rp1.010.000 (10-07-2024)

Sapphire Full-frequency Dynamic Driver - Dual Driver Two-way Crossover UWBS Combination Verified Acoustic FEA Optimization.

Powered two-way crossover + acoustic FEA optimization, verified by repeated testing, seamslessly couples the 10mm dynamic driver and 6mm planar magnetic driver, making full use of the characteristics of both and restoring the details of the music.

author: Knowledge Zenith Store
title: Knowledge Zenith KZ ZST X Dual Driver Earphone with MIC
description:
Rp189.000 (10-07-2024)

KZ ZST X bisa dibilang refreshment model dari KZ ZST yang popular sejak 2 tahun lalu. Secara fisik KZ ZST dan KZ ZST X bisa dikatakan sama. Perbedaaan terletak pada penggunaan silver cable dan warna dan Font yang lebih eye catching.

Selain dari sisi model Dynamic Driver pada KZ ZST X sudah diupgrade menggunakan 10mm dual magnetic driver. Dynamic driver ini untuk menghandle suara frekuensi rendah (bass) dan suara frekuensi tengah (vokal). Sedangkan untuk frekuensi tinggi (treble) masih menggunakan BA Driver 30095

author: Eagle Indonesia
title: Knowledge Zenith Earphones - KZ-ZSE - Dual Driver - With Mic
description:
Rp82.000 (10-07-2024)

The highly popular super-budget-friendly ZSE model by KZ is another milestone in KZ's catalogue that proved once more that great sound quality can be achieved for a very low price. Blatantly V-shaped, but with a rather stuggling bass response, that barely manages to not crackle by deep bass content. 

Sound signature-wise, I would call these earphones "ROCK Zircon without the steroids", since the mids and treble are so similar, but Zircon's bass is just so much more powerful and stable than ZSE's bass (which also means that ZSE's mids are less overrun by the bass).-audiobudget.com

author: csi-zone
title: Moondrop Golden Ages Planar True Wireless / TWS LDAC In Ear Earphone
description:
Rp1.299.000 (10-07-2024)

Superlinear Full-frequency Double-suspension Annular 13mm Planar Magnetic Driver

A newly designed 13mm planar magnetic driver with an annular magnetic circuit and annular diaphragm, in conjunction with a magnetic circuit array composed of several N55 high-performance neodymium magnets, together with an annular tiled driving circuit.

LC3 (Standard) Low-latency High-definition Audio Transport Protocol

The LC3 encoding and decoding protocol supporting the new generation Bluetooth LE Audio, when paired with devices that are also compatible with standard LC3, achieves not only much lower latency than traditional Bluetooth but also excellent high-fidelity signal transmission.

author: Knowledge Zenith Store
title: KZ AST new KZ Flagship 12 BA Driver Earphone with MIC
description:
Rp1.849.000 (10-07-2024)

Secara umum KZ AST masih membawa karakter driver BA yang detail monster namun lebih halus dan nyaman digunakan dalam waktu yang lebih lama.

Low / Bass
Oleh karena KZ AST menggunakan full BA dan dikarenakan dari karakter dari BA, jadi penggemar bass akut atau bass head kurang di rekomendasikan menggunakan earphone ini. Bass dari KZ AST mempunyai resolusi yang baik, bertekstur dan ketat namun masih punchy.

Mid / Vocal
Suara Vokal yang dihasilkan smooth tidak shouty seperti pada ZSN series, walaupun smooth namun vokal yang dihasilkan mempunyai detail yang baik dan kaya nuansa. Suara vokalnya juga terdengar penuh, berbodi dan tidak kopong.

High / Treble
Pada umumnya KZ terkenal dengan treblenya yang harsh dan mettalic terutama pada ZSN series, kalau sensitif treble bisa menyebabkan ear fatique dan gejala lainnya. Namun pada KZ AST treblenya smooth, walaupun smooth KZ AST memiliki treble extension dan clarity yang baik tanpa ada kesan sibillance.

Specification:
1. Product Name: KZ - AST
2. Impedance: 30Ω
3. Earphone sensitivity: 103dB/mW
4. Frequency range: 10-40.000Hz
5. Interface: 3.5mm
6.Cable Lngth: 1.25±0.05m
7.Earphone interface: 2Pin 0.75mm type C gold-plated

author: Sony Audio Official
title: SONY IER-Z1R Signature Series In-ear Headphones / Z1R
description:
Rp23.999.000 (10-07-2024)

Originally designed to make you feel
We designed the drivers in the IER-Z1R headphones from the ground up, to work in total harmony together. The consistent sound signature carried out across each driver works as if they were a perfect single driver.

Hear everything with a frequency response to 100kHz
The super tweeter in the IER-Z1R was developed to deliver ultra-high frequency extension with a new aluminum-coated LCP diaphragm and external magnetic circuit. Its ultra-fast response faithfully follows the fast dynamic transience of music, which provides you with live concert hall atmosphere

Naturally controlled acoustics
The vast experience and sense of our engineers is the key to acoustic design, which delivers the most natural sound. The finely tuned IER-Z1R acoustic structure steers audio from the trio of driver units as though they were a single, ideal driver.

author: Sony Audio Official
title: SONY WF-1000XM5 Silver Noise Canceling Truly Wireless / WF1000XM5
description:
Rp4.099.000 (10-07-2024)

The Best Noise Cancelling Headphones
Perangkat ini memiliki dua prosesor eksklusif Sony yang meredam lebih banyak noise eksternal dari sebelumnya

Dynamic Driver X
unit driver yang dirancang khusus, menyediakan reproduksi frekuensi lebar, memungkinkan bass yang lebih dalam, vokal halus, dan detail halus yang ditingkatkan, terutama pada instrumen bernada tinggi

Best Call Quality Ever
Berkat algoritme pereduksi bising berbasis AI berdasarkan pemrosesan Deep Neural Network (DNN), dan sensor konduksi tulang, suara Anda akan terdengar jelas dan lebih alami, bahkan di lingkungan yang bising.

author: Sony Audio Official

Nikmati kenyamanan sepanjang hari tanpa gangguan suara apapun
Dengan teknologi Noise Cancelling, desain ringan, dan daya tahan baterai yang tahan lama, Anda bisa menikmati musik lebih lama dan tanpa gangguan latar belakang.
